{"tid":793503,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以令自己開心啲","createTime":"2018-08-25T13:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T13:38:33.000Z","uid":98624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2cde25dccb8a9112934ceb2889720e9db518f9e1","tid":793503,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"個人好廢，啲人成日話我自卑，但自覺自己就係無咩做得好<br />\n前途又覺得好似無乜希望<br />\n朋友又不是多，班粉人一有男女朋友就唔撚見晒影，一係就出去玩又唔叫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩車個班我又無咩心機去同佢地熟，始終個年紀差太遠無咩話題<br />\n開心既淨係得望住自己啲寵物，自己遊下車河，但依啲只係得一瞬間，好快就無<br />\n以前好鍾意去旅行，但依排覺得去得個幾日又要返嚟香港好無癮好無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ca2f6ac98b1d5cbb66fce2c452b06993ac8e29","tid":793503,"uid":10609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b62f11e36ab320a5a5244ba01aa19502959788","tid":793503,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ca2f6ac98b1d5cbb66fce2c452b06993ac8e29","tid":793503,"uid":10609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"越嚟越覺得自己好無希望<br />\n好撚失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee539be445d4f2db307f7da8c28ce04600f2e306","tid":793503,"uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"Call G"},{"pid":"c472c4ae4c2977aa06e3a633e8b60e805f0620c6","tid":793503,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee539be445d4f2db307f7da8c28ce04600f2e306","tid":793503,"uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"Call G"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:22:04.000Z","msg":"玩下一皇三后<br />\n<br />\n包你開心哂"},{"pid":"52cc104794c141b71bf5912895c